race.comment: OH LANA (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (25.25) in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning four races. Worth another chance. JUMBUK DAMIEN (7) was in traffic last time here and failed to finish. No luck latest and can bounce back. BROCKY SANDS (2) turned in a plain run last time when sixth at this track over 510m behind UNLEASH ZAC (29.84) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Goes well out of this box with a win and five minor placings. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. MAGICAL PAWS (8) among the chances again based on last run here.
